Miip.

A floating character that you can play around with, and helps you make your phone more accessible and useful.

Tools to be made available :

Night time : 
1. Suggests you to set alarm clock, flash light and ask for reminders for tmrw.

Morning time :
1. Says hello with a funny joke. View calender, set reminders for today.

Evening time : 
1. Wishes you to go and play. Or listen to music.

A MiipInbox


